16:08Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Anish Athalye\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"me@anishathalye.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2023-02-27T12:16:08Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"anishathalye\\\",\\\"id\\\":3526486,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/anishathalye\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3526486?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"anishathalye\\\",\\\"id\\\":3526486,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/anishathalye\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3526486?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"6e7a1574b3a5f726f65966fc397aca5f88ade444\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/commit/6e7a1574b3a5f726f65966fc397aca5f88ade444\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Text inside pre is visible while printing as pdf.\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Henrik Zenkert\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"henrik.zenkert@gmail.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2023-02-27T09:35:51Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Henrik Zenkert\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"henrik.zenkert@gmail.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2023-02-27T09:35:51Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"YesSeri\\\",\\\"id\\\":34012616,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/YesSeri\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/34012616?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"YesSeri\\\",\\\"id\\\":34012616,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/YesSeri\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/34012616?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"fffa09e13ed0ca0db7955ef9a5f90f306c81774b\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/commit/fffa09e13ed0ca0db7955ef9a5f90f306c81774b\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"Merge branch 'findyy99/master'\\\\n\\\\nzsh doesn't have a default location for history (`HISTFILE` is unset).\\\\nOn macOS, it defaults to `~/.zsh_history`, even when `.zshrc` doesn't\\\\nexist (and no setup assistant runs), so I think they modified zsh to\\\\nbehave this way. On Debian 11 / zsh 5.8, the zsh setup assistant runs\\\\nwhen there is no ~/.zshrc, and if the user uses the interactive setup\\\\nassistant, the default is actually `HISTFILE=~/.histfile`, but the\\\\n\\\\\\\"configuration recommended by the system administrator\\\\\\\" (the\\\\n`/etc/zshrc`) has `HISTFILE=${ZDOTDIR:-$HOME}/.zsh_history`.\\\\n\\\\nThat being said, changing the text to say `.zsh_history` seems\\\\nreasonable.\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Anish Athalye\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"me@anishathalye.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2023-02-24T10:58:52Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Anish Athalye\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"me@anishathalye.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2023-02-24T10:58:52Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"anishathalye\\\",\\\"id\\\":3526486,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/anishathalye\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3526486?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"anishathalye\\\",\\\"id\\\":3526486,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/anishathalye\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3526486?v=4\\\"}},{\\\"sha\\\":\\\"230b01cc4617b7ef4c901a417daaab68d702d21b\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/missing-semester/commit/230b01cc4617b7ef4c901a417daaab68d702d21b\\\",\\\"commit\\\":{\\\"message\\\":\\\"change `.zhistory` to `.zsh_history`\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"Echoo\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"2110065578@qq.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2023-02-24T03:25:43Z\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"name\\\":\\\"GitHub\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"noreply@github.com\\\",\\\"date\\\":\\\"2023-02-24T03:25:43Z\\\"}},\\\"author\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"findyy99\\\",\\\"id\\\":26852735,\\\"profile_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/findyy99\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/26852735?v=4\\\"},\\\"committer\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"web-flow\\\",\\\"id\\\":19864447,\\\"profile_url\\\"